graph TB
    %% Development Environment Physical Architecture
    %% Core Flow: Users → API Gateway → Services → Database

    Users[Mobile/Web Users] --> APIGW[Azure API Management\nDeveloper Tier]

    subgraph AKS[Azure Kubernetes Service - Development]
        APIGW --> AuthSvc[AUTH Service Pod\nNode.js]
        APIGW --> SchdSvc[SCHD Service Pod\nNode.js]
        APIGW --> PlceSvc[PLCE Service Pod\nNode.js]
        APIGW --> MntrSvc[MNTR Service Pod\nNode.js]
        APIGW --> BrifSvc[BRIF Service Pod\nNode.js]
        APIGW --> AltnSvc[ALTN Service Pod\nNode.js]
        APIGW --> PaySvc[PAY Service Pod\nNode.js]

        AuthSvc --> PostgreSQL[(PostgreSQL Pod\n16GB Storage)]
        SchdSvc --> PostgreSQL
        PlceSvc --> PostgreSQL
        MntrSvc --> PostgreSQL
        BrifSvc --> PostgreSQL
        AltnSvc --> PostgreSQL
        PaySvc --> PostgreSQL

        PlceSvc --> Redis[(Redis Pod\nMemory Cache)]
        MntrSvc --> Redis

        SchdSvc --> ServiceBus[Azure Service Bus\nBasic Tier]
        MntrSvc --> ServiceBus
        BrifSvc --> ServiceBus
        AltnSvc --> ServiceBus
    end

    subgraph NodePool[Node Pool]
        Node[2x Standard B2s\n2 vCPU / 4GB RAM]
    end

    subgraph ExternalAPIs[External APIs]
        GooglePlaces[Google Places API]
        OpenWeather[OpenWeatherMap API]
        GoogleDirections[Google Directions API]
        FCM[Firebase FCM]
        PaymentGW[Payment Gateway\nToss Payments]
    end

    PlceSvc --> GooglePlaces
    MntrSvc --> GooglePlaces
    MntrSvc --> OpenWeather
    MntrSvc --> GoogleDirections
    BrifSvc --> FCM
    PaySvc --> PaymentGW
